{
  "name": "Expert Wizard",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/sundries/books/book-embossed-clasp-gold-brown.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Wizard Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell School Initiate</span></strong></span></p><ul><li><p>You learn 1 additional Arcane Spell from the chosen School.</p></li><li><p><strong>Signature School:</strong> When you cast a Spell from the chosen School, you can reduce its MP cost by an additional 1.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Arcane Sigil</span></strong></span></p><p>When you create a Sigil, you can add the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Spell Tag:</strong> (X MP) The Sigil gains an additional Spell School or Spell Tag per MP spent.</p></li><li><p><strong>Area:</strong> (X MP) The diameter of the Sigil increases by 1 Space per MP spent.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Prepared Spell</span></strong></span></p><p>When you complete a Long Rest, choose 1 additional Spell you know. Both Spells become your Prepared Spells until your next Long Rest.</p><p><em><strong>DC Tip:</strong> You can still only use Mana Limit Break once, on either of your Prepared Spells.</em></p>",
